# Project Rules

## Architecture
- Main API: `create_environment()` returns 3 callables
- LLM calls use DSPy with Gemini backend
- DSPy modules for query_agent and tool_mocker (optimizable)
- Traces normalized to `TraceSchema` before use

## File Organization
- `src/` - Core library code
- `examples/` - Runnable demos with sample data
- `data/` - User trace data (gitignored except .gitkeep)
- `docs/` - Technical documentation

## Dependencies
- Keep minimal (hackathon constraint)
- No ML frameworks (just numpy)
- Gemini SDK for all LLM needs

## Testing
- Run examples as smoke tests: `python examples/customer_service.py`
- Check imports work: `python -c "from src import create_environment"`
